### REST Client requests for local backend


@host = http://localhost:4000
# Paste a token here for manual testing, or leave empty and use the curl snippet below
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjQ3ZmExMWUxLTgxMmEtNGRlZS1hZmUwLTNiMjU4ZTRmNzM4NiIsIm5vbWUiOiJMdWlzIEFsYmVydG8gQ2FydmFsaG8gR29tZXMiLCJlbWFpbCI6Imx1aXMuY2dvbWVzMUBvdXRsb29rLmNvbSIsInRpcG8iOiJhbHVubyIsInN0YXR1cyI6ImF0aXZvIiwiaWF0IjoxNzYwMTIzNjM4LCJleHAiOjE3NjAxNTI0Mzh9.jBPwqL3-dj5-vlpgr_23eRy2ZBgISmJUgnfF1cOF9Uk

# qrcode token (will be returned by GET /api/carteirinhas/minha-carteirinha/:alunoId)
@token_qrcode = 6e4700d1-0735-4dfd-8374-363a54c10df5

# Example alunoId (replace with actual id from GET /api/alunos/me)
@alunoId = 47fa11e1-812a-4dee-afe0-3b258e4f7386

###
# 1) Login (use this to obtain a token and paste into @token)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"email": "luis.cgomes1@outlook.com",
	"senha": "0089@Luis"
}

# Optional (bash) quick token extraction (runs in your terminal, not REST Client):
# curl -s -X POST {{host}}/api/auth/login -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"email":"luis.cgomes1@outlook.com","senha":"0089@Luis"}' | jq -r '.token' | xargs -I{} printf "export TOKEN=%s\n" "{}"
# After running the line above in bash, you can use $TOKEN in subsequent curl commands.

###
# 2) Marcar presença (aluno autenticado)
# - Este endpoint usa o token do usuário (Authorization header). Não precisa body.
POST {{host}}/api/presencas/marcar-presenca
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


###
# 2.a) Obter dados do usuário autenticado (inclui aluno/usuario id)
GET {{host}}/api/alunos/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# 3) Confirmar presença (ida) via QR token
POST {{host}}/api/presencas/confirmar-embarque
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"token": "{{token_qrcode}}"
}

###
# 4) Confirmar presença (volta) via QR token
POST {{host}}/api/presencas/confirmar-volta
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"token": "{{token_qrcode}}"
}

###
# 5) Obter carteirinha ativa (para pegar o qrcode_token)
# - Substitua {{alunoId}} pelo ID do aluno ou use o token de sessão para obter o alunoId antes
GET {{host}}/api/carteirinhas/minha-carteirinha/{{alunoId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


